PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> 
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>  
PREFIX ub: <http://cs.uga.edu#> 
SELECT *  
FROM <http://www.cs.uga.edu#> 
WHERE 
{ 
    ?x a ub:GraduateStudent .  
    ?y a  ub:University .  
    ?z a ub:Department .  
    ?x ub:memberOf ?z .  
    ?z ub:subOrganizationOf ?y .  
 }
